var tipuesearch = {"pages": [{'title': 'About', 'text': "This website is created by a beginner student who wants to build an FPV system with as little money as possible. \n I don't want to use commercially available TX/RX modules or flight control chips. Instead, I want to use  STM32  and cheap sensors to build everything by myself. \n I think I will face many difficulties, but I hope I will learn a lot from this project. Wish me good luck,BTW my english is not well ,so sometime i will use wrong word or chinese . \n 2026/03/08 \n", 'tags': '', 'url': 'About.html'}, {'title': 'How to do data analysis', 'text': '\n \n 拿到原始數據。 \n \n 先看一眼數據長什麼樣，知道有沒有亂七八糟的東西（例如數字被當文字、很多空值、極端怪值）。 \n \n \n 把數據洗乾淨，明顯錯的極端值，用箱型圖或簡單規則刪/修正（例如電力消耗量負值就刪）。 \n \n \n 決定目標（y）和特徵（X），機器學習就是要用 X 猜 y。 \n \n \n （選做）把數據做一些調整（特徵工程）EX:數字太大或太小 → 標準化（減平均除標準差)。目標 y 如果差很大 → 可以先取 log（之後再轉回來。 \n \n \n 把資料分成「訓練用」和「測試用」，把 70～80% 當訓練，20～30% 當測試，測試資料不能拿來訓練，這樣才能知道模型在「沒看過的資料」上表現如何 \n \n \n 選一個模型 + 訓練它 \n \n \n 用測試資料做預測 \n \n \n 算迴歸誤差指標\xa0MAE MSE RMSE MAPE MPE R² \n \n \n 看結果 + 決定下一步 \n 看數字：MAE/RMSE 夠小嗎？R² 有沒有超過 0.7～0.8？ \n 如果不好 → 回到第 3～7 步改（加特徵、換模型、調參數、清洗更乾淨…） \n \n \n \n \n 迴歸模型誤差指標完整教學 \n  KaTeX CSS  \n \n  KaTeX JS  \n \n \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'How to do data analysis.html'}, {'title': 'regression error metric', 'text': '\n 1.error metric \n \n MAE\xa0 平均絕對誤差\xa0: 對真實值-預測值(誤差) 取絕對值後(黃色直線距離)相加， 再 平均。 \n MAE = 1 n ∑ i = 1 n ∣ 真實值 i − 預測值 i ∣ \\text{MAE} = \\frac{1}{n} \\sum_{i=1}^{n} \\left| \\text{真實值}_i - \\text{預測值}_i \\right| \n \n \n \n \n \n MSE\xa0 均方誤差\xa0: 對誤差平方(正方形面積)相加後再平均。 \n MSE = 1 n ∑ i = 1 n ( 真實值 i − 預測值 i ) 2 \\text{MSE} = \\frac{1}{n} \\sum_{i=1}^{n} \\left( \\text{真實值}_i - \\text{預測值}_i \\right)^2 \n \n \n \xa0 \xa0 \xa0 \xa0 \xa0 \xa0 \n \n RMSE\xa0 均方根誤差: 對誤差平方(正方形面積)相加後，平均再開根號。 \n RMSE = 1 n ∑ i = 1 n ( 真實值 i − 預測值 i ) 2   \n \n \n \n \n MPE 平均百分比誤差:(實際值-預測值)/ 實際值*100% 後取平均。 \n MPE = 1 n ∑ i = 1 n 真實值 i − 預測值 i 真實值 i × 100 % \\text{MPE} = \\frac{1}{n} \\sum_{i=1}^{n} \\frac{\\text{真實值}_i - \\text{預測值}_i}{\\text{真實值}_i} \\times 100\\% \n \n \n \n \n MAPE\xa0 平均絕對百分比誤差 :abs( (實際值-預測值 )/ 實際值*100% 後取平均 \n MAPE = 1 n ∑ i = 1 n ∣ 真實值 i − 預測值 i 真實值 i ∣ × 100 % \\text{MAPE} = \\frac{1}{n} \\sum_{i=1}^{n} \\left| \\frac{\\text{真實值}_i - \\text{預測值}_i}{\\text{真實值}_i} \\right| \\times 100\\% \n \n \n \n 2.goodness of fit \n \n  R²決定係數 \n \n \n \n \n 符號 \n 全名 \n 公式 \n 意思 \n \n \n \n \n SST \n Total Sum of Squares \n sum((y - mean(y)).^2) \n y 的總變異 \n \n \n SSR \n Regression Sum of Squares \n sum((y_pred - mean(y)).^2) \n 模型解釋到的變異 \n \n \n SSE \n Error Sum of Squares \n sum((y - y_pred).^2) \n 模型沒解釋到的變異（殘差） \n \n \n \n \n \n *mean(y)為原始數據取平均，\xa0 y為某一點的原始數據, y_pred為某一點預測方程式的值。 \n SST=SSR+SSE; \n R 2 = 1 − ∑ ( 某一點的原始數據 − 某一點預測方程式的值 ) 2 ∑ ( 某一點的原始數據 − 原始數據取平均 ) 2 = 1 − 殘差平方和 (SSR) 總平方和 (SST) R^2 = 1 - \\frac{\\sum \\left( \\text{某一點的原始數據} - \\text{某一點預測方程式的值} \\right)^2}{\\sum \\left( \\text{某一點的原始數據} - \\text{原始數據取平均} \\right)^2} = 1 - \\frac{\\text{殘差平方和 (SSR)}}{\\text{總平方和 (SST)}} \n \n \n \n \n Q:數值多少算好 \n A: \n \n \n \n 指標 \n 單位 \n 越小越好？ \n 對大誤差（outlier）的敏感度 \n 什麼情況下「看起來小」才算好？ \n 常見應用場景建議 \n \n \n \n \n MAE \n 跟 y 相同單位 \n 是 \n 低（robust） \n 跟 y 的平均值或範圍比，小於 5–15% 左右常被接受 \n 業務容易理解、對大錯不特別懲罰 \n \n \n MSE \n y 單位的平方 \n 是 \n 極高 \n 很難直接看，通常只跟其他模型比 \n 訓練時用（可微分） \n \n \n RMSE \n 跟 y 相同單位 \n 是 \n 高 \n 常比 MAE 大一點，跟 y 平均值比，小於 10–20% 常被接受 \n 最常用（平衡解釋力與懲罰大錯） \n \n \n MAPE \n 百分比 (%) \n 是 \n 中等（但 y 接近 0 會爆炸） \n <10% 優秀、10–20% 好、20–50% 可接受、>50% 通常偏差 \n 銷售、需求預測（規模無關） \n \n \n MPE \n 百分比 (%) \n 接近 0 最好 \n 中等（有正負） \n 接近 0（有系統性偏誤時會遠離 0） \n 檢查是否有 bias \n \n \n \n \n Q:MAE RMSE 數值會差不多嗎? \n A: \n 情況一：誤差都差不多大 err = [1, 1, 1, 1, 1] MAE = 1.0 RMSE = 1.0 ← 幾乎一樣 \n 情況二：有一個很大的離群誤差  err = [1, 1, 1, 1, 10]  MAE = 2.8  RMSE = 4.6 ← 差很多，因為 10² = 100 被放大了 \n \n Q:R² 決定係數 — 多少算好？ \n A: \n \n R² > 0.9–0.95：優秀（物理模型強的領域） \n R² 0.8–0.9：良好（大多數工程應用） \n R² 0.6–0.8：可接受（現場數據噪音大） \n R² < 0.6：通常不夠好，除非是極端複雜系統 \n \n \n \n \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'regression error metric.html'}, {'title': 'cameraSistyem', 'text': '', 'tags': '', 'url': 'cameraSistyem.html'}, {'title': 'Single_Board_PTZ', 'text': 'i using ARDUINO IDE remeber stm32 PA10 connect to GND \n 實驗順序 \n \n Servo 角度對應到的ADC值 \n GY85給SERVO的原始數值，此時Servo的ADC值 \n 用matlab判斷低通率波alpha值 \n GY85給SERVO的數值低通 濾波 \n 用matlab驗證角度精確度 \n 把ARDUINO改成閉迴路。 \n \n \n 順序2 發現數值抖動太多且雜訊太大，所以變成， 順序4 GY85給SERVO的數值低通 濾波 \n 順序3.因為順序2是濾波後的 數值， 所以用matlab找alpha就沒意義了 \n 日誌 \n \n 2026-03-13 完成順序1. \n 2026-03-15 完成順序2. 但發現數值抖動太多 \n 2026-03-17\xa0完成順序3.但alpha值 RMAS有19.多 \n 2026-03-18 懷疑是順序1 ployfit太爛，回去改 \n 2026-03-19 發現不是順序1 ployfit沒問題應該是順序2要濾波 \n 2026-03-27 做完順序4.GY85濾波後運作速度跟得上且震盪我可以接受，接下來驗證角度精確度就好 \n 2026-03-29\xa0做完順序5.  matlab每次重新跑偏移值都會變，所以接下來就是把ARDUINO改成閉迴路。 \n 2026-04-02 完成 順序6 但PID 始終調不好 \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'Single_Board_PTZ.html'}, {'title': 'fail', 'text': '這裡的思路是把servo 對應到的ADC 找出來用線性擬合，找到每個角度對應到的ADC值，但問題就在這裡，數據中 \n 顯示Servo 內建電位計在高角度區嚴重劣化，低角度區（30~90度）追蹤還算可以，但高角度區（>110度）ADC值嚴重偏差EX:150°：883、929、865、891 → 平均約 892，波動 ±32 導致偏移5度左右(死區5.)。 \n 讓線性擬合在高角度區徹底失效，導致後面調PID時一到 高角度區就會需要很長時間才回正，且有太多係數相關連導致調整有難度，所以一直卡在， 高角度區追蹤不良 、調參困難這個死循環。 \n 解決方法 \n A:換一顆好 Servo，外接角度感測器 \n B: 線性擬合變分段線性擬合 \n C:直接用 ADXL345 量到的角度直接 myServo.write()，放棄Servo ADC \n \n 我這裡選 C 因為我對角度準確度沒有很要求，且我希望反應速度快，不震盪。 \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'fail.html'}, {'title': 'angle2Servo_ADC_Data', 'text': '\n 這裡是用來找servo ADC對應到servo的角度 並用測試資料驗證 \n 用MAE RMSE R² 來推測模型好不好 \n 結論 : \n 一次曲線就夠用,但有些角度跟測試資料差很多 看原始資料發現他原本ADC就會亂飄 \n 導致模型大概+-5° \n 所以接下來加入"中位數濾波"看會不會好點 \n \n 但我已經 mean 了應該沒問題了阿，換median也差不多 \n 問題應該不在這應該在GY85控制servo那要濾波 \n \n \n divide SG90 and using a electric wire to contect Variable resistor \n \n \n Code \n #include<Servo.h>\n\nServo myservo;\n\nint pos = 0; \n\nvoid setup(){\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n  myservo.attach(PA0);\n  \n  delay(1000);\n\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  for (pos = 60; pos <= 150; pos +=30) { \n    \n    myservo.write(pos);             \n    delay(1000);     \n\n    myservo.detach();\n\n    Serial.print(pos);\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.println(analogRead(PA7));\n    delay(100);   \n    myservo.attach(PA0);                    \n  }\n  for (pos = 120; pos >= 30; pos -= 30) {\n    myservo.write(pos);  \n    delay(1000);  \n\n    myservo.detach();\n    Serial.print(pos);\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.println(analogRead(PA7));\n    delay(100);       \n    myservo.attach(PA0);               \n  }\n} \n Result \n /downloads/servo_angle_ADC.txt \n /downloads/find_data.txt \n Matlab find avarge2(2026/03/19) \n %{\n2026/03/17\n用來找servo ADC對應到servo的角度 並用測試資料驗證\n用MAE RMSE R² 來推測模型好不好\n結論 :\n一次曲線就夠用,但有些角度跟測試資料差很多 看原始資料發現他原本ADC就會亂飄\n模型大概+-5°\n2026/03/19\n但我已經 mean 了應該沒問題了阿，換 median也差不多\n%}\n\nclc; clear; close all;\n\nfigPos = [100 100 900 600];   % 視窗大小，可調\noffset = 30;                  % 每個視窗偏移，避免完全重疊\n%% 讀取校正資料\norg_data = readmatrix(\'servo_angle_ADC.txt\', \'Delimiter\', \',\');\nangle_raw = org_data(:,1);\nadc_raw   = org_data(:,2);%這裡直接用原始 ADC，沒有濾波\n\n\n\n%% 先按角度平均（去除重複影響）\nunique_angles = unique(angle_raw);%unique();把()中的矩陣的每個元素小到大排列\nadc_avg = zeros(size(unique_angles));\ncount    = zeros(size(unique_angles));%用來計算每個角度有幾筆數據\nfor i = 1:length(unique_angles)\n    mask = (angle_raw == unique_angles(i));%這個角度出現的所有位置 回傳true ...\n    % 讓mask變成一邏輯矩陣 EX[0 ,1 ,0 ,0]\n    \n    adc_avg(i) = median(adc_raw(mask));      % 只對這個角度中位數濾波          \n    count(i)  = sum(mask);\nend\n\nangle = unique_angles\';   % 轉成列向量（ polyfit 喜歡列向量）\nadc   = adc_avg\';\n\n\n%% 顯示中位數結果\nfprintf(\'\\n=== 中位數結果 ===\\n\');\nfprintf(\'角度\\t筆數\\t中位數 ADC\\n\');\nfor i = 1:length(unique_angles)\n    \n        fprintf(\'%d°\\t%d\\t%.2f\\n\', unique_angles(i), count(i), adc_avg(i));\n    \nend\n\n%% 畫長條圖\nfigure(\'Name\', \'原始散佈圖\',\'Position\',figPos + [0 5*offset 0 0]);\nb = bar(unique_angles, adc_avg, \'FaceColor\', [0.3 0.7 0.9]);\nxlabel(\'角度 (度)\');\nylabel(\'平均 ADC 值\');\ntitle(\'各角度平均 ADC 值\');\ngrid on;\nset(gca, \'XTick\', unique_angles, \'XTickLabelRotation\', 45);\n\n%新增：在每根柱子上方顯示 ADC 值\nxVal = b.XData;\nyVal = b.YData;\nfor i = 1:length(xVal)\n    text(xVal(i), yVal(i) + 10, sprintf(\'%.0f\', yVal(i)), ...\n        \'HorizontalAlignment\', \'center\', ...\n        \'FontSize\', 9, ...\n        \'FontWeight\', \'bold\');\nend\n\n%% 擬合模型：angle = f(ADC)\np_lin = polyfit(adc, angle, 1);   % 一次曲線\np_quad = polyfit(adc, angle, 2);  % 二次曲線\n%% 顯示擬合方程式（注意 polyfit 最高次在前）\nfprintf(\'=== 擬合結果 ===\\n\');\nfprintf(\'一次擬合： angle = %.6f × ADC + %.6f\\n\', p_lin(1), p_lin(2));\nfprintf(\'二次擬合： angle = %.6e × ADC² + %.6f × ADC + %.6f\\n\', ...\n        p_quad(1), p_quad(2), p_quad(3));\n\n%% 在原始數據上計算預測角度 & 誤差指標\n% 每個角度濾波後的 adc 重新展開，對應回 angle_raw\nadc_filtered_full = zeros(size(adc_raw));\nfor i = 1:length(unique_angles)\n    mask = (angle_raw == unique_angles(i));\n    adc_this = adc_raw(mask);\n    adc_this = medfilt1(adc_this, 7);\n    adc_filtered_full(mask) = adc_this;   % 存回對應位置\nend\n\n% 驗證時用濾波後的資料\nangle_pred_lin_raw  = polyval(p_lin,  adc_filtered_full);\nangle_pred_quad_raw = polyval(p_quad, adc_filtered_full);\n\n\nerr_lin_raw  = angle_pred_lin_raw  - angle_raw;\nerr_quad_raw = angle_pred_quad_raw - angle_raw;\n\nmae_lin  = mean(abs(err_lin_raw));\nmae_quad = mean(abs(err_quad_raw));\n\nrmse_lin  = sqrt(mean(err_lin_raw.^2));\nrmse_quad = sqrt(mean(err_quad_raw.^2));\n\nfprintf(\'\\n=== 原始數據上的誤差 (單位：度) ===\\n\');\nfprintf(\'一次擬合 → MAE = %.4f°   RMSE = %.4f°\\n\', mae_lin, rmse_lin);\nfprintf(\'二次擬合 → MAE = %.4f°   RMSE = %.4f°\\n\', mae_quad, rmse_quad);\n\n%% R²\nSS_tot       = sum((angle_raw - mean(angle_raw)).^2);\nSS_res_lin   = sum(err_lin_raw.^2);\nSS_res_quad  = sum(err_quad_raw.^2);\nR2_lin  = 1 - SS_res_lin  / SS_tot;\nR2_quad = 1 - SS_res_quad / SS_tot;\n\nfprintf(\'\\nR² (linear)    = %.6f\\n\', R2_lin);\nfprintf(\'R² (quadratic) = %.6f\\n\', R2_quad);\n\n%% 讀取測試資料\ndata = readmatrix(\'find_data.txt\', \'Delimiter\', \',\');\nADC_test = data(:,2);\n%% 畫原始散佈圖\nfigure(\'Name\',\'原始散佈圖\',\'Position\',figPos + [0 4*offset 0 0]);\nscatter(adc_raw, angle_raw, 60, \'filled\', \'MarkerFaceColor\',\'b\');\nxlabel(\'ADC value\'); ylabel(\'Angle (deg)\');\ntitle(\'原始散佈圖與擬合模型\');\nset(gca, \'FontSize\', 12);\n\n\n%% 產生平滑曲線用\nx_fit = linspace(min(adc), max(adc), 300);\ny_lin  = polyval(p_lin,  x_fit);\ny_quad = polyval(p_quad, x_fit);\n\nhold on;\nplot(x_fit, y_lin,  \'r-\', \'LineWidth\', 2.2, \'DisplayName\', \'Linear fit\');\nplot(x_fit, y_quad, \'g-\', \'LineWidth\', 2.2, \'DisplayName\', \'Quadratic fit\');\nlegend(\'show\', \'Location\',\'northwest\');\nhold off;\n\n\n\n%% 對測試資料反推角度\nfprintf(\'\\n=== 測試資料反推角度 ===\\n\');\nangle_test_lin  = polyval(p_lin,  ADC_test);\nangle_test_quad = polyval(p_quad, ADC_test);\n\n%% 看所有預測數據\n% 全部資料 (linear)\ndisp(\'所有預測結果 (linear)：\');\ndisp(\'   ADC       預測角度 (線性)\');\ndisp([ADC_test angle_test_lin]);\n\n% 全部資料 (quadratic)\ndisp(\' \');\ndisp(\'所有預測結果 (quadratic)：\');\ndisp(\'   ADC       預測角度 (二次)\');\ndisp([ADC_test angle_test_quad]); \n Matlab find avarge \n %{\n2026/03/17\n用來找servo ADC對應到servo的角度 並用測試資料驗證\n用MAE RMSE R² 來推測模型好不好\n結論 :\n一次曲線就夠用,但有些角度跟測試資料差很多 看原始資料發現他原本ADC就會亂飄\n模型大概+-5°\n%}\n\nclc; clear; close all;\n\nfigPos = [100 100 900 600];   % 視窗大小，可調\noffset = 30;                  % 每個視窗偏移，避免完全重疊\n%% 讀取校正資料\norg_data = readmatrix(\'servo_angle_ADC.txt\', \'Delimiter\', \',\');\nangle_raw = org_data(:,1);\nadc_raw   = org_data(:,2);\n\n%% 先按角度平均（去除重複影響）\nunique_angles = unique(angle_raw);%unique();把()中的矩陣的每個元素小到大排列\nadc_avg = zeros(size(unique_angles));\ncount    = zeros(size(unique_angles));%用來計算每個角度有幾筆數據\nfor i = 1:length(unique_angles)\n    mask = (angle_raw == unique_angles(i));%這個角度出現的所有位置 回傳true ...\n    % 讓mask變成一邏輯矩陣 EX[0 ,1 ,0 ,0]\n    adc_avg(i) = mean(adc_raw(mask));%把這個角度出現的raw 給ADC用\n    count(i)    = sum( mask);\nend\n\nangle = unique_angles\';   % 轉成列向量（ polyfit 喜歡列向量）\nadc   = adc_avg\';\n%% 顯示平均結果\nfprintf(\'\\n=== 平均結果 ===\\n\');\nfprintf(\'角度\\t筆數\\t平均 ADC\\n\');\nfor i = 1:length(unique_angles)\n    \n        fprintf(\'%d°\\t%d\\t%.2f\\n\', unique_angles(i), count(i), adc_avg(i));\n    \nend\n%% 擬合模型：angle = f(ADC)\np_lin = polyfit(adc, angle, 1);   % 一次曲線\np_quad = polyfit(adc, angle, 2);  % 二次曲線\n%% 顯示擬合方程式（注意 polyfit 最高次在前）\nfprintf(\'=== 擬合結果 ===\\n\');\nfprintf(\'一次擬合： angle = %.6f × ADC + %.6f\\n\', p_lin(1), p_lin(2));\nfprintf(\'二次擬合： angle = %.6e × ADC² + %.6f × ADC + %.6f\\n\', ...\n        p_quad(1), p_quad(2), p_quad(3));\n\n%% 在原始數據上計算預測角度 & 誤差指標\nangle_pred_lin_raw  = polyval(p_lin,  adc_raw);\nangle_pred_quad_raw = polyval(p_quad, adc_raw);\n\nerr_lin_raw  = angle_pred_lin_raw  - angle_raw;\nerr_quad_raw = angle_pred_quad_raw - angle_raw;\n\nmae_lin  = mean(abs(err_lin_raw));\nmae_quad = mean(abs(err_quad_raw));\n\nrmse_lin  = sqrt(mean(err_lin_raw.^2));\nrmse_quad = sqrt(mean(err_quad_raw.^2));\n\nfprintf(\'\\n=== 原始數據上的誤差 (單位：度) ===\\n\');\nfprintf(\'一次擬合 → MAE = %.4f°   RMSE = %.4f°\\n\', mae_lin, rmse_lin);\nfprintf(\'二次擬合 → MAE = %.4f°   RMSE = %.4f°\\n\', mae_quad, rmse_quad);\n\n%% R²\nSS_tot       = sum((angle_raw - mean(angle_raw)).^2);\nSS_res_lin   = sum(err_lin_raw.^2);\nSS_res_quad  = sum(err_quad_raw.^2);\nR2_lin  = 1 - SS_res_lin  / SS_tot;\nR2_quad = 1 - SS_res_quad / SS_tot;\n\nfprintf(\'\\nR² (linear)    = %.6f\\n\', R2_lin);\nfprintf(\'R² (quadratic) = %.6f\\n\', R2_quad);\n%% 畫長條圖\nfigure(\'Name\', \'原始散佈圖\',\'Position\',figPos + [0 5*offset 0 0]);\nb = bar(unique_angles, adc_avg, \'FaceColor\', [0.3 0.7 0.9]);\nxlabel(\'角度 (度)\');\nylabel(\'平均 ADC 值\');\ntitle(\'各角度平均 ADC 值\');\ngrid on;\nset(gca, \'XTick\', unique_angles, \'XTickLabelRotation\', 45);\n\n% ← 新增：在每根柱子上方顯示 ADC 值\nxVal = b.XData;\nyVal = b.YData;\nfor i = 1:length(xVal)\n    text(xVal(i), yVal(i) + 10, sprintf(\'%.0f\', yVal(i)), ...\n        \'HorizontalAlignment\', \'center\', ...\n        \'FontSize\', 9, ...\n        \'FontWeight\', \'bold\');\nend\n\n%% 讀取測試資料\ndata = readmatrix(\'find_data.txt\', \'Delimiter\', \',\');\nADC_test = data(:,2);\n%% 畫原始散佈圖\nfigure(\'Name\',\'原始散佈圖\',\'Position\',figPos + [0 4*offset 0 0]);\nscatter(adc_raw, angle_raw, 60, \'filled\', \'MarkerFaceColor\',\'b\');\nxlabel(\'ADC value\'); ylabel(\'Angle (deg)\');\ntitle(\'原始散佈圖與擬合模型\');\nset(gca, \'FontSize\', 12);\n\n\n%% 產生平滑曲線用\nx_fit = linspace(min(adc), max(adc), 300);\ny_lin  = polyval(p_lin,  x_fit);\ny_quad = polyval(p_quad, x_fit);\n\nhold on;\nplot(x_fit, y_lin,  \'r-\', \'LineWidth\', 2.2, \'DisplayName\', \'Linear fit\');\nplot(x_fit, y_quad, \'g-\', \'LineWidth\', 2.2, \'DisplayName\', \'Quadratic fit\');\nlegend(\'show\', \'Location\',\'northwest\');\nhold off;\n\n\n\n%% 對測試資料反推角度\nfprintf(\'\\n=== 測試資料反推角度 ===\\n\');\nangle_test_lin  = polyval(p_lin,  ADC_test);\nangle_test_quad = polyval(p_quad, ADC_test);\n\n%% 看所有預測數據\n% 全部資料 (linear)\ndisp(\'所有預測結果 (linear)：\');\ndisp(\'   ADC       預測角度 (線性)\');\ndisp([ADC_test angle_test_lin]);\n\n% 全部資料 (quadratic)\ndisp(\' \');\ndisp(\'所有預測結果 (quadratic)：\');\ndisp(\'   ADC       預測角度 (二次)\');\ndisp([ADC_test angle_test_quad]); \n Result \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n === 平均結果 === 角度 筆數 平均 ADC 30° 136 224.66 40° 136 267.86 50° 136 320.90 60° 136 361.23 70° 136 416.03 80° 136 456.01 90° 136 506.29 100° 136 543.71 110° 136 597.64 120° 136 640.64 130° 136 696.01 140° 136 735.22 150° 136 776.62 \n === 擬合結果 === 一次擬合： angle = 0.215583 × ADC + -18.501444 二次擬合： angle = 6.319533e-06 × ADC² + 0.209235 × ADC + -17.097761 === 校正點上的誤差 (單位：度) === 一次擬合 → MAE = 0.6768° RMSE = 0.8215° 二次擬合 → MAE = 0.6736° RMSE = 0.8041° R² (linear) = 0.999518 R² (quadratic) = 0.999538 === 測試資料反推角度 === \n 所有預測結果 (linear)：  ADC 預測角度 (線性)  370.0000 61.2642  469.0000 82.6069  617.0000 114.5132  703.0000 133.0533  616.0000 114.2976  490.0000 87.1341  348.0000 56.5214  234.0000 31.9449  346.0000 56.0902  488.0000 86.7030  648.0000 121.1962  768.0000 147.0662  645.0000 120.5495  495.0000 88.2121  320.0000 50.4851  229.0000 30.8670  344.0000 55.6590  503.0000 89.9367  620.0000 115.1599  768.0000 147.0662  648.0000 121.1962  496.0000 88.4276  350.0000 56.9525  223.0000 29.5735  361.0000 59.3240  512.0000 91.8770  659.0000 123.5676   所有預測結果 (quadratic)：  ADC 預測角度 (二次)  370.0000 61.1844  469.0000 82.4236  617.0000 114.4061  703.0000 133.1177  616.0000 114.1891  490.0000 86.9448  348.0000 56.4814  234.0000 32.2093  346.0000 56.0542  488.0000 86.5140  648.0000 121.1402  768.0000 147.3223  645.0000 120.4880  495.0000 88.0221  320.0000 50.5046  229.0000 31.1485  344.0000 55.6270  503.0000 89.7464  620.0000 115.0573  768.0000 147.3223  648.0000 121.1402  496.0000 88.2376  350.0000 56.9087  223.0000 29.8760  361.0000 59.2597  512.0000 91.6873  659.0000 123.5327 \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'angle2Servo_ADC_Data.html'}, {'title': 'LPF_GY85_2_servo(Open_Loop)', 'text': '\n matlab每次重新跑偏移值都會變，所以接下來就是把它改成閉迴路。 \n \n \n \n 開迴路系統：GY-85 → 低通濾波 → 轉 Servo 指令角 → Servo 動作 → ADC 回授 → 中位數 + 低通濾波 → 轉實際角度 → MATLAB 分析誤差 → 加補償 \n \n \n ARDUINO CODE \n #include <Wire.h>\n#include <Servo.h>\n\nServo myServo;\n\nunsigned long lastTime = 0;\n\n#define ADXL345 0x53\n\nint16_t offset_x = 0, offset_y = 0, offset_z = 0;\n\n// ================== 濾波相關變數 ==================\nfloat filtered_roll = 0.0;        // EMA 濾波後的 roll\nfloat alpha_roll = 0.24;          // 指令端 alpha（可調）\n\n// Servo ADC 濾波\nconst int median_size = 5;\nint adc_buffer[median_size] = {0};//等於0矩陣\nint buffer_idx = 0;\nfloat filtered_adc_angle = 90.0;\nfloat alpha_adc = 0.10;           // ADC 端 alpha 為了讓實際角度讀值平滑，去除馬達負載造成的凸波（spike）和雜訊（主要用在 MATLAB 分析）\n\n\n// ================== 新增：Servo 偏移補償 ==================\nfloat servo_offset = 25.01;     // 這裡填入 MATLAB 算出的平均偏移值\n\n// =================================================\nint16_t readAxis(byte reg);\nvoid cailbrate();\n\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n  Wire.setSCL(PB8);\n  Wire.setSDA(PB9);\n  Wire.begin();\n  delay(1000);\n\n  // ================== 初始化 ADXL345 ================== \n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(0x2D); Wire.write(0x08); Wire.endTransmission();\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(0x31); Wire.write(0x00); Wire.endTransmission();\n\n  Serial.println("ADXL345 ready");\n\n  myServo.attach(PA0);\n  myServo.write(90);\n  Serial.println("Servo ready");\n\n  cailbrate();\n  \n  // ================== 輸出標題 ================== \n  //GY_TO_servo_angle vs ADC_filtered → 可以看指令角度和實際角度的差距（追蹤誤差）\n  //filtered_roll vs raw_roll → 可以看低通濾波的效果\n  //ADC_raw vs ADC_filtered → 可以看中位數濾波去凸波的效果\n  Serial.println("millis, GY_TO_servo_angle, compensated_angle,  ADC_raw,ADC_filtered, filtered_roll,  raw_roll");\n  \n  delay(500);\n  lastTime = micros();\n}\nvoid loop() {\n   if(micros() - lastTime >= 10000){ // 10000us = 10ms\n  lastTime += 10000;\n\n    // ================== 讀取三軸資料 ================== \n    float x = readAxis(0x32) - offset_x;\n    float y = readAxis(0x34) - offset_y;\n    float z = readAxis(0x36) - offset_z;\n\n    float x_g = x / 256.0;\n    float y_g = y / 256.0;\n    float z_g = z / 256.0;\n\n    // ================== 計算原始 roll（未濾波） ================== \n    float raw_roll = atan2(y_g, sqrt(x_g * x_g + z_g * z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n    // ================== 對 GY85 指令端做 低通 濾波 ================== \n    filtered_roll = alpha_roll * raw_roll + (1 - alpha_roll) * filtered_roll;\n\n    // ================== 轉成 servo 角度（建議範圍 30~150，避免撞極限） ================== \n    int GY_TO_servo_angle = map(constrain((int)filtered_roll, -60, 60), -60, 60, 30, 150);\n\n    // ================== 新增補償：加上 servo_offset ==================\n    int compensated_angle = GY_TO_servo_angle + (int)servo_offset;   // 四捨五入轉 int\n    compensated_angle = constrain(compensated_angle, 30, 150);       // 限制範圍避免撞極限\n\n    // ================== 對 Servo ADC 做 中位數 + 低通 濾波 ================== \n    int raw_adc = analogRead(PA7);\n    adc_buffer[buffer_idx] = raw_adc;\n    buffer_idx = (buffer_idx + 1) % median_size;//更新索引，讓下一次寫入時指向下一個位置。索引 到達 4 的時候，下一次就會回到 0。\n\n    // ================== 取中位數去凸波 ================== \n    int temp[median_size];\n    for (int i = 0; i < median_size; i++) temp[i] = adc_buffer[i];\n    sort(temp, median_size);// 排序副程式在最下面\n    int median_adc = temp[median_size / 2];// 第 3 個值就是中位數（最中間的）\n\n    // ================== ADC 轉角度 + 低通 平滑 ================== \n    float adc_angle = 0.215583 * median_adc - 18.501444;\n    filtered_adc_angle = alpha_adc * adc_angle + (1 - alpha_adc) * filtered_adc_angle;\n\n    // ================== 驅動伺服 ================== \n    myServo.write(compensated_angle);//改成補償後的指令角度\n\n    // ================== 輸出 ==================\n    Serial.print(millis());\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.print(GY_TO_servo_angle);           // 指令角度\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.print(compensated_angle);           //補償後的指令角度\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.print(raw_adc);                     // 原始 ADC（觀察凸波）\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.print((int)filtered_adc_angle);     // 濾波後實際角度\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.print(filtered_roll, 3);            // 濾波後的 roll\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.println(raw_roll, 3);               // 原始 roll（未濾波）\n\n  }\n}\n\n// ================== 輔助函式 ==================\nint16_t readAxis(byte reg) {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345); \n  Wire.write(reg);  // 指向 DATAX0 暫存器（X 軸低位元組）\n  Wire.endTransmission(false);// 保持連線，準備讀取\n  Wire.requestFrom(ADXL345, 2);\n    // 請求 2 個位元組（LSB + MSB）\n    // I2C 每次只能傳 8 位元，所以 16 位元的 X 軸數值\n    // 被 ADXL345 拆成兩個暫存器分兩次傳送\n  if (Wire.available() >= 2) {// 確認 2 個位元組都已收到\n    byte lsb = Wire.read();// 第一次讀 → DATAX0 低位元組\n    byte msb = Wire.read();// 第二次讀 → DATAX1 高位元組\n    // 將兩個位元組重新拼合成完整的 16 位元數值\n    // 為什麼要拆開又合起來？\n    // 因為 I2C 硬體限制每次只能傳 8 位元\n    // ADXL345 被迫把 16 位元數值拆成兩半分兩次送出\n    // 所以我們收到後必須自己拼回來：\n    //\n    // msb      = 00000010          （高 8 位元）\n    // msb << 8 = 00000010 00000000 （推到高位）\n    // | lsb    = 00000010 00000001 （填入低 8 位元）\n    // 結果     = 513    \n    return (int16_t)((msb << 8) | lsb);\n  }\n  return 0;\n}\n\n//校正階段 找offset\nvoid cailbrate() {\n  Serial.print("校正中 保持靜止...");\n  long sum_x = 0, sum_y = 0, sum_z = 0;\n  for (int i = 0; i < 500; i++) {\n    sum_x += readAxis(0x32);\n    sum_y += readAxis(0x34);\n    sum_z += readAxis(0x36);\n    delay(10);\n  }\n  offset_x = sum_x / 500;\n  offset_y = sum_y / 500;\n  offset_z = sum_z / 500 - 256;\n  Serial.println("校正完成");\n}\n\n// 小排序函式（用於中位數濾波）\nvoid sort(int arr[], int n) {\n  for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {\n    for (int j = 0; j < n - i - 1; j++) {\n      if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1]) {\n        int temp = arr[j];\n        arr[j] = arr[j + 1];\n        arr[j + 1] = temp;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n} \n \n MATLAB CODE \n clc; clear; close all;\n%% 1. 讀取資料 用 MATLAB 錄製序列埠資料\ns = serialport("COM3", 115200);  \nconfigureTerminator(s, "LF");\n\ndata = [];\ndisp("開始錄製，按 Ctrl+C 停止...");\n\nfor i = 1:2000  % 錄 2000 筆 = 約 20 秒\n    line = readline(s);\n    nums = str2double(split(line, ","));\n    if length(nums) == 7\n        data = [data; nums\'];\n    end\nend\n\nsave("servo_data.mat", "data");\ndisp("錄製完成");\n\nload("servo_data.mat");\n\nt               = data(:,1) / 1000;  % ms 轉成秒\nGY_TO_servo_angle  = data(:,2);      % 指令角度\ncompensated_angle  = data(:,3);      % 補償後指令角度\nADC_raw         = data(:,4);         % 原始 ADC\nADC_filtered    = data(:,5);         % 濾波後實際角度\nfiltered_roll   = data(:,6);         % 濾波後 roll\nraw_roll        = data(:,7);         % 原始 roll\n\n%% 2. 確認濾波效果\nfigure(\'Name\',\'濾波效果\');\nsubplot(2,1,1);\nplot(t, raw_roll, \'r\', t, filtered_roll, \'b\', \'LineWidth\', 1.5);\nlegend(\'raw roll\', \'filtered roll\');\ntitle(\'Roll 濾波效果\');\nxlabel(\'時間 (s)\'); ylabel(\'角度 (°)\');\ngrid on;\n\nsubplot(2,1,2);\nplot(t, ADC_raw, \'r\', t, ADC_filtered, \'b\', \'LineWidth\', 1.5);\nlegend(\'ADC raw\', \'ADC filtered\');\ntitle(\'ADC 濾波效果\');\nxlabel(\'時間 (s)\'); ylabel(\'ADC 值\');\ngrid on;\n\n%% 3. 指令 vs 實際角度 + 平均偏移計算（專為補償用）\nfigure(\'Name\',\'指令 vs 實際角度 - 偏移補償\');\n\nplot(t, GY_TO_servo_angle, \'b\', \'LineWidth\', 1.5);   \nhold on;\nplot(t, ADC_filtered, \'r\', \'LineWidth\', 1.5);\n\nerror = ADC_filtered - GY_TO_servo_angle  ;        % 實際 - 指令\nmean_offset = mean(error);                       % 補償值\nrmse = sqrt(mean(error.^2));\nmax_error = max(abs(error));\n\nyline(mean_offset, \'k--\', \'LineWidth\', 1.2);\n\nlegend(\'指令角度 (GY→Servo)\', \'實際角度 (ADC)\', ...\n       [\'平均偏移 = \' num2str(mean_offset, \'%.3f\') \' °\']);\n\ntitle(\'指令 vs 實際角度（建議補償值）\');\nxlabel(\'時間 (s)\'); ylabel(\'角度 (°)\');\ngrid on;\n\n% 在 Command Window 顯示結果\nfprintf(\'\\n=== Servo 偏移補償建議 ===\\n\');\nfprintf(\'平均偏移 (Mean Bias)     : %.3f 度\\n\', mean_offset);\nfprintf(\'均方根誤差 (RMSE)        : %.3f 度\\n\', rmse);\nfprintf(\'最大絕對誤差             : %.3f 度\\n\', max_error);\n\n%% 4.指令 vs 實際角度（改用 compensated_angle 來分析補償效果）\nfigure(\'Name\',\'補償後 指令 vs 實際角度\');\n\nplot(t, compensated_angle, \'b\', \'LineWidth\', 1.5);   % 使用補償後的角度\nhold on;\nplot(t, ADC_filtered, \'r\', \'LineWidth\', 1.5);\n\nerror = ADC_filtered - compensated_angle ; \nmean_offset = mean(error);\nrmse = sqrt(mean(error.^2));\nmax_error = max(abs(error));\n\nyline(mean_offset, \'k--\', \'LineWidth\', 1.2);\n\nlegend(\'補償後指令角度\', \'實際角度 (ADC)\', ...\n       [\'平均偏移 = \' num2str(mean_offset, \'%.3f\') \' °\']);\n\ntitle(\'補償後 指令 vs 實際角度\');\nxlabel(\'時間 (s)\'); ylabel(\'角度 (°)\');\ngrid on;\n\nfprintf(\'\\n=== 補償後誤差統計 ===\\n\');\nfprintf(\'平均偏移     : %.3f 度\\n\', mean_offset);\nfprintf(\'RMSE         : %.3f 度\\n\', rmse);\nfprintf(\'最大絕對誤差 : %.3f 度\\n\', max_error); \n \n ==================結果 ================== \n 開始錄製，按 Ctrl+C 停止... \n \n 錄製完成 \n \n === Servo 偏移補償建議 === \n 平均偏移 (Mean Bias) : 28.866 度 \n 均方根誤差 (RMSE) : 39.191 度 \n 最大絕對誤差 : 115.000 度 \n \n === 補償後誤差統計 === \n 平均偏移 : 7.661 度 \n RMSE : 24.594 度 \n 最大絕對誤差 : 90.000 度 \n \n \n \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'LPF_GY85_2_servo(Open_Loop).html'}, {'title': 'discard_GY85_2_SERVO_original_data', 'text': '/downloads/gy85_servo_data.txt \n #include<Wire.h>\n#include<Servo.h>\n\nServo myServo;\n\nunsigned long lastTime = 0;\n\n\n#define ADXL345 0x53\n\nint16_t offset_x =0;\nint16_t offset_y =0;\nint16_t offset_z =0;\n\n\n\nint16_t readAxis(byte );\nvoid cailbrate();\n\nvoid setup(){\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n\n  Wire.setSCL(PB8);\n  Wire.setSDA(PB9);\n  Wire.begin();\n  delay(1000);\n\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(0x2D);\n  Wire.write(0x08);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(0x31);\n  Wire.write(0x00);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n\n  Serial.println("ADXL345 ready");\n\n  delay(100);\n  \n  myServo.attach(PA0);\n  myServo.write(90);\n  Serial.println("Servo ready");\n  delay(1000);\n\n  cailbrate();\n  Serial.println("millis  GY_TO_servo_angle   ADC  ");\n  delay(100);\n}\n\n\nvoid loop() {\n   if(micros() - lastTime >= 10000){ // 10000us = 10ms\n  lastTime += 10000;\n    \n    // 讀取三軸並減去偏移\n    float x = readAxis(0x32) - offset_x;\n    float y = readAxis(0x34) - offset_y;\n    float z = readAxis(0x36) - offset_z;\n\n    // 換算成 g（±2g 量程，256 LSB/g）\n    float x_g = x / 256.0;\n    float y_g = y / 256.0;\n    float z_g = z / 256.0;\n\n    // 計算 Pitch 和 Roll\n    // Pitch：前後傾斜角度\n    // Roll ：左右傾斜角度\n    float pitch = atan2(x_g, sqrt(y_g * y_g + z_g * z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n    float roll  = atan2(y_g, sqrt(x_g * x_g + z_g * z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n    int GY_TO_servo_angle = map(constrain((int)roll,-90,90),-90,90 ,30,150);\n// constrain (輸入值, 最小, 最大)     EX:輸入值<最小 ,輸入值=最小\n// map (輸入值, 輸入最小值, 輸入最大值, 輸入最小值對應到的輸出最小值, 輸入最大值對應到的輸出最大值)\nmyServo.write(GY_TO_servo_angle);\n\nSerial.print(millis());\nSerial.print(",");\nSerial.print(GY_TO_servo_angle);\nSerial.print(",");\nSerial.println(analogRead(PA7));\n\n    }\n}\n////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////\nint16_t readAxis(byte reg){\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(reg);\n  Wire.endTransmission(false);\n  Wire.requestFrom(ADXL345,2);\n  if(Wire.available()>=2){\n    byte lsb =Wire.read();\n    byte msb =Wire.read();\n    return (int16_t)((msb << 8) | lsb); \n  }else\n    return 0;\n}\n\nvoid cailbrate(){\n  Serial.print("校正中 保持靜止");\n  long sum_x=0,sum_y=0,sum_z=0;\n\n  for(int i=0;i<500;i++){\n    sum_x += readAxis(0x32);\n    sum_y += readAxis(0x34);\n    sum_z += readAxis(0x36);\n    delay(10);\n  }\n  offset_x =sum_x /500;\n  offset_y =sum_y /500;\n  offset_z =sum_z /500 - 256;//水平時Z為256(1g)\n\n  Serial.println("校正完成");\n} \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'discard_GY85_2_SERVO_original_data.html'}, {'title': 'LPF_GY85_2_servo(close_loop)', 'text': '#include <Wire.h>\n#include <Servo.h>\n\nServo myServo;\n\nunsigned long lastTime = 0;\n\n#define ADXL345 0x53\n\nint16_t offset_x = 0, offset_y = 0, offset_z = 0;\n\n// ================== 濾波相關變數 ==================\nfloat filtered_roll = 0.0;        // 濾波後的 roll\nfloat alpha_roll = 0.25;          // 指令端 alpha（可調）\n\n// ================== Servo ADC 濾波 ==================\nconst int median_size = 9;\nint adc_buffer[median_size] = {0};//等於0矩陣\nint buffer_idx = 0;\nfloat filtered_adc_angle = 90.0;\nfloat alpha_adc = 0.18;           // ADC 端 alpha 為了讓實際角度讀值平滑，去除馬達負載造成的凸波（spike）和雜訊（主要用在分析）\n//越小  濾波越強，越大 減少延遲\n\n// ================== PID 控制變數 ==================\nfloat Kp = 2.;     //  P 值\nfloat Ki = 0.003;    // 積分增益\nfloat Kd = 0.0;     // 微分增益 但 alpha_adc 已有率波功能所以這裡先不用\n\nfloat integral = 0.0;         // 積分項累積\nfloat last_error = 0.0;       // 上一次誤差（用於微分）\nfloat error_deadband = 5.;   // 死區 之前 角度 to ADC 誤差差不多5度\n\nfloat prev_target = 0;        // 偵測目標角度有沒有變化\n\n// =================================================\nint16_t readAxis(byte reg);\nvoid cailbrate();\n\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n  Wire.setSCL(PB8);\n  Wire.setSDA(PB9);\n  Wire.begin();\n  delay(1000);\n\n  // ================== 初始化 ADXL345 ================== \n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(0x2D); Wire.write(0x08); Wire.endTransmission();\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(0x31); Wire.write(0x00); Wire.endTransmission();\n\n  Serial.println("ADXL345 ready");\n\n  myServo.attach(PA0);\n  myServo.write(90);\n  Serial.println("Servo ready");\n\n  cailbrate();\n\n  delay(500);\n  lastTime = micros();\n}\nvoid loop() {\n  if(micros() - lastTime >= 20000){   // 20ms 一次 SG90 更新 ≈ 50Hz\n    lastTime += 20000;\n\n    // ================== 讀取 ADXL345 ==================\n    float x = readAxis(0x32) - offset_x;\n    float y = readAxis(0x34) - offset_y;\n    float z = readAxis(0x36) - offset_z;\n\n    float x_g = x / 256.0;\n    float y_g = y / 256.0;\n    float z_g = z / 256.0;\n\n    float raw_roll = atan2(y_g, sqrt(x_g * x_g + z_g * z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n    // ==================濾波==================\n    filtered_roll = alpha_roll * raw_roll + (1 - alpha_roll) * filtered_roll;\n\n    // ==================開迴路指令角度==================\n    filtered_roll = constrain(filtered_roll, -60, 60);//filtered_roll範圍±60 \n\n    float GY_TO_servo_angle =\n        (filtered_roll + 60.0) * (150.0 - 30.0) / 120.0 + 30.0;//把filtered_roll範圍改成0~120\n        //線性映射公式y = (x - xmin) * (ymax - ymin) / (xmax - xmin) + ymin\n        //(x - xmin)/ (xmax - xmin)把 x 壓到0~1\n        //× (ymax - ymin)放大到新範圍\n        //+ ymin +平移\n        GY_TO_servo_angle = constrain(GY_TO_servo_angle, 30, 150);\n\n    // ================== ADC 讀取與濾波 ==================\n    int raw_adc = analogRead(PA7);\n    adc_buffer[buffer_idx] = raw_adc;\n    buffer_idx = (buffer_idx + 1) % median_size;\n\n    int temp[median_size];\n    for (int i = 0; i < median_size; i++) temp[i] = adc_buffer[i];\n    sort(temp, median_size);\n    int median_adc = temp[median_size / 2];\n    \n    float adc_angle = 0.215583 * median_adc - 18.501444 -8.; //加上offset 偏移\n\n    filtered_adc_angle = alpha_adc * adc_angle + (1 - alpha_adc) * filtered_adc_angle;\n\n    // ================== 誤差計算 ==================\n\n    if (abs(GY_TO_servo_angle - prev_target) > 2.0) {\n      integral = 0;  // 目標變了，清掉積分\n      }\n      prev_target = GY_TO_servo_angle;\n\n    float error = GY_TO_servo_angle - filtered_adc_angle;     // 誤差 = 指令角度 - 濾波後實際角度\n\n    if(abs(error) < error_deadband){ //防小誤差一直積分\n      error = 0;\n      integral *= 0.85;  // 死區內積分衰減\n      }\n    else{\n      error -= (error > 0 ? error_deadband : -error_deadband);\n      }\n\n    // ================== PID 計算 ==================\n    integral += error * 0.02;                    // 0.02 秒 = 20ms\n    float derivative = (error - last_error) / 0.02;\n\n    // 限制積分項（抗積分飽和）\n    integral = constrain(integral, -15, 15);\n\n    float pid_output = Kp * error + Ki * integral + Kd * derivative;\n\n   // ================== 最終輸出 ==================\n    int compensated_angle = (int)(GY_TO_servo_angle + pid_output);\n    compensated_angle = constrain(compensated_angle, 25, 155);                       \n    \n\n    // ==================驅動 Servo==================\n    myServo.write(compensated_angle);\n   \n\n    // ================== 序列埠輸出（方便調參） ==================\n    Serial.print(GY_TO_servo_angle, 1);           // 指令角度\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.print(filtered_adc_angle, 1);          // 實際角度\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.print(error, 2);                       // 誤差\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.print(pid_output, 2);                  // PID 輸出值\n    Serial.print(",");\n    Serial.println(compensated_angle);            // 最終送給 servo 的角度\n\n    last_error = error;\n  }\n}\n\n// ================== 輔助函式 ==================\nint16_t readAxis(byte reg) {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345); \n  Wire.write(reg);  // 指向 DATAX0 暫存器（X 軸低位元組）\n  Wire.endTransmission(false);// 保持連線，準備讀取\n  Wire.requestFrom(ADXL345, 2);\n    // 請求 2 個位元組（LSB + MSB）\n    // I2C 每次只能傳 8 位元，所以 16 位元的 X 軸數值\n    // 被 ADXL345 拆成兩個暫存器分兩次傳送\n  if (Wire.available() >= 2) {// 確認 2 個位元組都已收到\n    byte lsb = Wire.read();// 第一次讀 → DATAX0 低位元組\n    byte msb = Wire.read();// 第二次讀 → DATAX1 高位元組\n    // 將兩個位元組重新拼合成完整的 16 位元數值\n    // 為什麼要拆開又合起來？\n    // 因為 I2C 硬體限制每次只能傳 8 位元\n    // ADXL345 被迫把 16 位元數值拆成兩半分兩次送出\n    // 所以我們收到後必須自己拼回來：\n    //\n    return (int16_t)((msb << 8) | lsb);\n  }\n  return 0;\n}\n\n//校正階段 找offset\nvoid cailbrate() {\n  Serial.print("校正中 保持靜止...");\n  long sum_x = 0, sum_y = 0, sum_z = 0;\n  for (int i = 0; i < 500; i++) {\n    sum_x += readAxis(0x32);\n    sum_y += readAxis(0x34);\n    sum_z += readAxis(0x36);\n    delay(10);\n  }\n  offset_x = sum_x / 500;\n  offset_y = sum_y / 500;\n  offset_z = sum_z / 500 - 256;\n  Serial.println("校正完成");\n}\n\n// 小排序函式（用於中位數濾波）\nvoid sort(int arr[], int n) {\n  for (int i = 0; i < n - 1; i++) {\n    for (int j = 0; j < n - i - 1; j++) {\n      if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1]) {\n        int temp = arr[j];\n        arr[j] = arr[j + 1];\n        arr[j + 1] = temp;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n} \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'LPF_GY85_2_servo(close_loop).html'}, {'title': 'success', 'text': '\n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'success.html'}, {'title': 'raw', 'text': '#include <Wire.h>\n#include <Servo.h>\n\nServo myServo;\n\nunsigned long lastTime = 0;\n\n#define ADXL345 0x53\n\nint16_t offset_x = 0, offset_y = 0, offset_z = 0;\n\n// ================== 濾波相關變數 ==================\nfloat filtered_roll = 0.0;\nfloat alpha_roll = 0.35;   //alpha 越小 濾波越強 延遲越大 反之\n\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n  Wire.setSCL(PB8);\n  Wire.setSDA(PB9);\n  Wire.begin();\n  delay(1000);\n\n  //==================初始化 ADXL345==================\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(0x2D); Wire.write(0x08); Wire.endTransmission();\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345);\n  Wire.write(0x31); Wire.write(0x00); Wire.endTransmission();\n\n  Serial.println("ADXL345 ready");\n\n  myServo.attach(PA0);\n  myServo.write(90);\n  Serial.println("Servo ready");\n\n  cailbrate();   \n  delay(500);\n  lastTime = micros();\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  if (micros() - lastTime >= 20000) {   // 50Hz 更新\n    lastTime += 20000;\n\n    //==================讀取 ADXL345==================\n    float x = readAxis(0x32) - offset_x;\n    float y = readAxis(0x34) - offset_y;\n    float z = readAxis(0x36) - offset_z;\n\n    float x_g = x / 256.0;\n    float y_g = y / 256.0;\n    float z_g = z / 256.0;\n\n    float raw_roll = atan2(y_g, sqrt(x_g * x_g + z_g * z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n    //==================低通濾波==================\n    filtered_roll = alpha_roll * raw_roll + (1 - alpha_roll) * filtered_roll;\n\n    //==================限制範圍==================\n    filtered_roll = constrain(filtered_roll, -60, 60);\n\n    //================== 映射到 Servo 可動範圍（30~150度）==================\n    int servo_angle = (int)((filtered_roll + 60.0) * (150.0 - 30.0) / 120.0 + 30.0);\n    servo_angle = constrain(servo_angle, 30, 150);\n\n    // ================== 驅動 Servo ==================\n    myServo.write(servo_angle);\n\n    //================== 序列埠輸出 ==================\n    Serial.print("Raw: ");\n    Serial.print(raw_roll, 1);\n    Serial.print("  Filtered: ");\n    Serial.print(filtered_roll, 1);\n    Serial.print("  Servo: ");\n    Serial.println(servo_angle);\n  }\n}\n\n// ================== 輔助函式 ==================\nint16_t readAxis(byte reg) {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345); \n  Wire.write(reg);  // 指向 DATAX0 暫存器（X 軸低位元組）\n  Wire.endTransmission(false);// 保持連線，準備讀取\n  Wire.requestFrom(ADXL345, 2);\n    // 請求 2 個位元組（LSB + MSB）\n    // I2C 每次只能傳 8 位元，所以 16 位元的 X 軸數值\n    // 被 ADXL345 拆成兩個暫存器分兩次傳送\n  if (Wire.available() >= 2) {// 確認 2 個位元組都已收到\n    byte lsb = Wire.read();// 第一次讀 → DATAX0 低位元組\n    byte msb = Wire.read();// 第二次讀 → DATAX1 高位元組\n    // 將兩個位元組重新拼合成完整的 16 位元數值\n    // 為什麼要拆開又合起來？\n    // 因為 I2C 硬體限制每次只能傳 8 位元\n    // ADXL345 被迫把 16 位元數值拆成兩半分兩次送出\n    // 所以我們收到後必須自己拼回來：\n    //\n    return (int16_t)((msb << 8) | lsb);\n  }\n  return 0;\n}\n\n//==================校正階段 找offset==================\nvoid cailbrate() {\n  Serial.print("校正中 保持靜止...");\n  long sum_x = 0, sum_y = 0, sum_z = 0;\n  for (int i = 0; i < 500; i++) {\n    sum_x += readAxis(0x32);\n    sum_y += readAxis(0x34);\n    sum_z += readAxis(0x36);\n    delay(10);\n  }\n  offset_x = sum_x / 500;\n  offset_y = sum_y / 500;\n  offset_z = sum_z / 500 - 256;\n  Serial.println("校正完成");\n} \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'raw.html'}, {'title': 'pitch_yaw', 'text': '#include <Wire.h>\n#include <Servo.h>\n#include <math.h>\n\n// ================== Servo 定義 ==================\nServo pitchServo;   // PA0\nServo yawServo;     // PA6\n\nunsigned long lastTime = 0;\n\n#define ADXL345_ADDR  0x53\n#define HMC5883L_ADDR 0x1E\n\n// ================== 校正偏移 ==================\nint16_t accel_offset_x = 0, accel_offset_y = 0, accel_offset_z = 0;\nfloat mag_offset_x = 0, mag_offset_y = 0;\n\n// ================== 零點誤差 ==================\nfloat pitch_zero_offset = 0.0;\nfloat yaw_zero_offset   = 0.0;\n\n// ================== 狀態控制 ==================\nbool servo_active = false;\n\n// ================== 濾波變數 ==================\nfloat filtered_pitch = 0.0;\nfloat filtered_roll  = 0.0;\nfloat filtered_yaw   = 0.0;\nfloat alpha_pitch = 0.35;\nfloat alpha_roll  = 0.35;\nfloat alpha_yaw   = 0.35;\n\n// ==========================================\n//              函式宣告\n// ==========================================\nvoid initADXL345();\nvoid initHMC5883L();\nint16_t readAxisLSB(byte addr, byte reg);\nvoid readAccel(float &x_g, float &y_g, float &z_g);\nvoid readMag(float &mx, float &my, float &mz);\nvoid calibrateAccel();\nvoid calibrateMag();\nvoid recordZeroPoint();\nint mapAngle(float angle);\n\n// ==========================================\n//              Setup\n// ==========================================\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n  Wire.setSCL(PB8);\n  Wire.setSDA(PB9);\n  Wire.begin();\n  delay(1000);\n\n  initADXL345();\n  initHMC5883L();\n\n  pitchServo.attach(PA0);\n  yawServo.attach(PA6);\n  pitchServo.write(90);\n  yawServo.write(90);\n  Serial.println("Servo ready (PA0=Pitch, PA6=Yaw)");\n\n  calibrateAccel();\n  calibrateMag();\n\n  Serial.println("=========================================");\n  Serial.println("指令：L = 鎖定Servo / S = 記錄零點並開始");\n  Serial.println("=========================================");\n\n  delay(500);\n  lastTime = micros();\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              Loop\n// ==========================================\nvoid loop() {\n\n  // ================== 鍵盤輸入 ==================\n  if (Serial.available()) {\n    char cmd = Serial.read();\n\n    // L：鎖定 Servo 在 90 度\n    if (cmd == \'L\' || cmd == \'l\') {\n      servo_active = false;\n      pitchServo.write(90);\n      yawServo.write(90);\n      Serial.println(">> Servo 已停在 90 度，請將頭擺正後輸入 \'S\'");\n    }\n\n    // S：記錄零點並開始\n    if (cmd == \'S\' || cmd == \'s\') {\n      recordZeroPoint();\n    }\n  }\n\n  // ================== 主迴圈 20ms ==================\n  if (micros() - lastTime >= 20000) {\n    lastTime += 20000;\n\n    // 讀取加速度計\n    float x_g, y_g, z_g;\n    readAccel(x_g, y_g, z_g);\n\n    // Pitch & Roll\n    float raw_pitch = atan2(-x_g, sqrt(y_g*y_g + z_g*z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n    float raw_roll  = atan2(y_g, z_g) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n    filtered_pitch = alpha_pitch * raw_pitch + (1.0 - alpha_pitch) * filtered_pitch;\n   filtered_roll  = alpha_roll  * raw_roll  + (1.0 - alpha_roll)  * filtered_roll;\n\n    // 讀取磁力計\n    float mx, my, mz;\n    readMag(mx, my, mz);\n\n    // 傾斜補償（含 Roll）\n    float pitch_rad = filtered_pitch * PI / 180.0;\n    float roll_rad  = filtered_roll  * PI / 180.0;\n\n    float mx_h = mx * cos(pitch_rad)\n               + my * sin(roll_rad) * sin(pitch_rad)\n               - mz * cos(roll_rad) * sin(pitch_rad);\n    float my_h = my * cos(roll_rad)\n               + mz * sin(roll_rad);\n\n    float raw_yaw = atan2(-my_h, mx_h) * 180.0 / PI;\n    filtered_yaw  = alpha_yaw * raw_yaw + (1.0 - alpha_yaw) * filtered_yaw;\n\n    // 套用零點誤差\n    float corrected_pitch = filtered_pitch - pitch_zero_offset;\n    float corrected_yaw   = filtered_yaw   - yaw_zero_offset;\n\n    corrected_pitch = constrain(corrected_pitch, -60, 60);\n    corrected_yaw   = constrain(corrected_yaw,   -60, 60);\n\n    // 只有 active 才驅動 Servo\n    if (servo_active) {\n      pitchServo.write(mapAngle(corrected_pitch));\n      yawServo.write(mapAngle(corrected_yaw));\n    }\n\n    // 序列埠輸出\n    Serial.print("Pitch: "); Serial.print(corrected_pitch, 1);\n    Serial.print("  Yaw: "); Serial.print(corrected_yaw, 1);\n    Serial.print("  PS: ");  Serial.print(servo_active ? mapAngle(corrected_pitch) : 90);\n    Serial.print("  YS: ");  Serial.print(servo_active ? mapAngle(corrected_yaw)   : 90);\n    Serial.print("  [");     Serial.print(servo_active ? "RUN" : "LOCK");\n    Serial.println("]");\n  }\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              初始化\n// ==========================================\nvoid initADXL345() {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x2D); Wire.write(0x08);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x31); Wire.write(0x00);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n  Serial.println("ADXL345 ready");\n}\n\nvoid initHMC5883L() {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x00); Wire.write(0x70); // 8avg, 15Hz\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n\n  Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x01); Wire.write(0x20); // Gain=1（±1.3 Ga）\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n\n  Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x02); Wire.write(0x00); // Continuous mode\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n  Serial.println("HMC5883L ready");\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              讀取\n// ==========================================\n\n// ADXL345：LSB first\nint16_t readAxisLSB(byte addr, byte reg) {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(addr);\n  Wire.write(reg);\n  Wire.endTransmission(false);\n  Wire.requestFrom(addr, (uint8_t)2);\n  if (Wire.available() >= 2) {\n    byte lsb = Wire.read();\n    byte msb = Wire.read();\n    return (int16_t)((msb << 8) | lsb);\n  }\n  return 0;\n}\n\nvoid readAccel(float &x_g, float &y_g, float &z_g) {\n  x_g = (readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x32) - accel_offset_x) / 256.0;\n  y_g = (readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x34) - accel_offset_y) / 256.0;\n  z_g = (readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x36) - accel_offset_z) / 256.0;\n}\n\n// HMC5883L：一次讀完 6 bytes，避免資料不同步\n// 暫存器順序：X(0x03), Z(0x05), Y(0x07)\nvoid readMag(float &mx, float &my, float &mz) {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x03);\n  Wire.endTransmission(false);\n  Wire.requestFrom(HMC5883L_ADDR, (uint8_t)6);\n\n  if (Wire.available() >= 6) {\n    int16_t raw_mx = (Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read();\n    int16_t raw_mz = (Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read(); // Z 在 Y 前面！\n    int16_t raw_my = (Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read();\n\n    mx = raw_mx - mag_offset_x;\n    my = raw_my - mag_offset_y;\n    mz = raw_mz;//Z 軸通常偏差較小，所以保留原始值\n  }\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              校正\n// ==========================================\nvoid calibrateAccel() {\n  Serial.println("加速度計校正中，保持靜止...");\n  long sum_x = 0, sum_y = 0, sum_z = 0;\n  for (int i = 0; i < 500; i++) {\n    sum_x += readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x32);\n    sum_y += readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x34);\n    sum_z += readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x36);\n    delay(10);\n  }\n  accel_offset_x = sum_x / 500;\n  accel_offset_y = sum_y / 500;\n  accel_offset_z = sum_z / 500 - 256;\n  Serial.println("加速度計校正完成");\n}\n\nvoid calibrateMag() {\n  float mx_max = -99999, mx_min = 99999;\n  float my_max = -99999, my_min = 99999;//一開始設極大/極小值，確保第一次更新一定會改變\n\n  // 第一步：等待開始\n  Serial.println("磁力計校正：輸入任意鍵開始擺頭 5 次 ...");\n  while (!Serial.available());\n  Serial.read();\n\n  Serial.println("開始擺頭 5 次！完成後再按任意鍵結束...");\n\n  // 第二步：持續收資料，直到再按一次鍵\n  while (true) {\n    // 有按鍵就結束\n    if (Serial.available()) {\n      Serial.read();\n      break;\n    }\n\n    Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n    Wire.write(0x03);\n    Wire.endTransmission(false);\n    Wire.requestFrom(HMC5883L_ADDR, (uint8_t)6);\n\n    if (Wire.available() >= 6) {\n      float raw_mx = (int16_t)((Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read());\n      (void)((Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read()); // skip Z\n      float raw_my = (int16_t)((Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read());\n\n      mx_max = max(mx_max, raw_mx); mx_min = min(mx_min, raw_mx);//max(a, b) 是 Arduino 內建函式，會回傳 a 和 b 中較大的那一個。\n      my_max = max(my_max, raw_my); my_min = min(my_min, raw_my);//min(a, b) 回傳兩個數中較小的那一個。\n    }\n\n    delay(30);\n  }\n\n  // 範圍檢查\n  float mx_range = mx_max - mx_min;\n  float my_range = my_max - my_min;\n  Serial.print("mx 範圍: "); Serial.print(mx_range);\n  Serial.print("  my 範圍: "); Serial.println(my_range);\n\n  if (mx_range < 50 || my_range < 50) {\n    Serial.println("警告：擺頭角度可能不足，建議重新校正！");\n  }\n\n  mag_offset_x = (mx_max + mx_min) / 2.0;\n  mag_offset_y = (my_max + my_min) / 2.0;\n\n  Serial.print("Mag offset X: "); Serial.print(mag_offset_x);\n  Serial.print("  Y: ");          Serial.println(mag_offset_y);\n  Serial.println("磁力計校正完成");\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              零點記錄\n// ==========================================\nvoid recordZeroPoint() {\n  // 讀取當前角度作為零點\n  float x_g, y_g, z_g;\n  readAccel(x_g, y_g, z_g);\n\n  float mx, my, mz;\n  readMag(mx, my, mz);\n\n  pitch_zero_offset = atan2(-x_g, sqrt(y_g*y_g + z_g*z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n  float pitch_rad = pitch_zero_offset * PI / 180.0;\n  float roll_rad  = atan2(y_g, z_g);\n\n  float mx_h = mx * cos(pitch_rad)\n             + my * sin(roll_rad) * sin(pitch_rad)\n             - mz * cos(roll_rad) * sin(pitch_rad);\n\n  float my_h = my * cos(roll_rad)\n             + mz * sin(roll_rad);\n             \n  yaw_zero_offset = atan2(-my_h, mx_h) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n  // 濾波初始值歸零，避免開始時突然跳動\n  filtered_pitch = 0.0;\n  filtered_roll  = 0.0;\n  filtered_yaw   = 0.0;\n\n  servo_active = true;\n\n  Serial.print(">> 零點記錄完成 — pitch_offset: ");\n  Serial.print(pitch_zero_offset, 1);\n  Serial.print("  yaw_offset: ");\n  Serial.println(yaw_zero_offset, 1);\n  Serial.println(">> Servo 開始跟隨頭部動作");\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              工具函式\n// ==========================================\nint mapAngle(float angle) {\n  return constrain((int)(angle + 90.0), 30, 150);\n} \n \n  [if mso]><br><![endif] \n  [if mso]><br><![endif] \n  [if mso]><br><![endif] \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'pitch_yaw.html'}, {'title': 'Tx _ Rx_PTZ', 'text': '使用兩塊 STM32，分別作為 發射端（Tx） 和 接收端（Rx），透過 NRF24L01(2.4GHz) 實現無線頭部姿態跟隨。 \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'Tx _ Rx_PTZ.html'}, {'title': 'example_NRF24L01', 'text': '\n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'example_NRF24L01.html'}, {'title': 'STM32F411 ESP8266 發送端程式與接收端程式', 'text': 'STM32F411發送端程式 \n 這段程式利用 STM32F411 搭配 nRF24L01 無線模組，透過按鈕控制訊號的發送。訊號會被另一端的接收器 ( ESP8266) 接收，用來驅動伺服馬達。 \n STM32F411 與 nRF24L01 \n \n \n CE → PA1 \n \n \n CSN → PA4 \n \n \n SCK → PA5 \n \n \n MISO → PA6 \n \n \n MOSI → PA7 \n \n \n \xa03.3V → 3.3V \n \n \n GND → GND \n \n \n 按鈕 ：\xa0PA0，使用內建上拉電阻。 \n LED ： PC13，作為狀態指示。 \n 其他 :STM32F411 3.3v GND 並聯一47uF電解電容，改善電源穩定性。 \n \n #include <SPI.h>          // 引入 SPI 通訊函式庫\n#include <nRF24L01.h>     // 引入 nRF24L01 無線模組定義\n#include <RF24.h>         // 引入 RF24 函式庫，方便操作 nRF24L01\n\n// 建立 RF24 物件，指定 CE 與 CSN 腳位\nRF24 radio(PA1, PA4);\n\n// 無線通訊管道地址，必須與接收端一致\nconst byte address[6] = "00001";\n\n// 按鈕與 LED 腳位\nconst int buttonPin = PA0;\nconst int ledPin    = PC13;\n\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(115200);   // 初始化序列埠，方便除錯\n  delay(2000);            // 延遲 2 秒，確保系統穩定\n\n  pinMode(buttonPin, INPUT_PULLUP); // 設定按鈕腳位，使用內建上拉電阻\n  pinMode(ledPin, OUTPUT);          // 設定 LED 腳位為輸出\n  digitalWrite(ledPin, HIGH);       // 預設 LED 亮起\n\n  // 指定 SPI 腳位 (STM32F411 的硬體 SPI 腳位)\n  SPI.setMOSI(PA7);\n  SPI.setMISO(PA6);\n  SPI.setSCLK(PA5);\n  SPI.begin();                      // 啟動 SPI\n  Serial.println("SPI 完成");\n\n  // 初始化 nRF24L01 無線模組\n  if (!radio.begin()) {\n    Serial.println("nRF24 初始化失敗！檢查接線");\n    while (1); // 停止程式，等待修正\n  }\n \n  // 確認晶片是否連線成功\n  if (radio.isChipConnected()) {\n    Serial.println("nRF24 晶片連線成功");\n  } else {\n    Serial.println("nRF24 晶片未偵測到");\n  }\n\n  // 設定無線模組參數\n  radio.openWritingPipe(address);   // 開啟發送管道\n  radio.setPALevel(RF24_PA_LOW);    // 設定功率等級 (低功率)\n  radio.setDataRate(RF24_1MBPS);    // 設定傳輸速率 (1Mbps)\n  radio.setChannel(76);             // 設定頻道 (必須與接收端一致)\n  radio.stopListening();            // 停止接收，進入發送模式\n\n  Serial.println("STM32F411 發送端啟動 - 按鈕準備好");\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  // 讀取按鈕狀態，按下時為 LOW → trigger = true\n  bool trigger = (digitalRead(buttonPin) == LOW);\n\n  // 嘗試發送 trigger 狀態到接收端\n  bool success = radio.write(&trigger, sizeof(trigger));\n\n  // 根據發送結果輸出訊息\n  if (success) {\n    Serial.println(trigger ? "正在發送：開始擺動" : "正在發送：停止擺動");\n  } else {\n    Serial.println("發送失敗...");\n  }\n\n  delay(50); // 每 50ms 更新一次狀態，避免過快\n}\n \n \xa0 \n ESP8266 接收端程式 \n 透過 ESP8266 搭配 nRF24L01 無線模組，接收來自 STM32F411 發送端的按鈕訊號，當接收到「開始擺動」訊號時，控制伺服馬達持續左右擺動，接收到「停止擺動」訊號時，伺服馬達停止更新角度。 \n ESP8266 與 nRF24L01 \n \n \n CE → D4 (GPIO2) \n \n \n CSN → D8 (GPIO15) \n \n \n SCK → D5 (GPIO14) \n \n \n MISO → D6 (GPIO12) \n \n \n MOSI → D7 (GPIO13) \n \n \n VCC → 3.3V (必須穩定供電，不能用 5V) \n \n \n GND → GND \n \n \n ESP8266 與伺服馬達 \n \n \n 訊號線 → D1 (GPIO5) \n \n \n VCC → 外部 5V 電源 (建議獨立供電，避免 ESP8266 電壓掉落) \n \n \n GND → 外部電源 GND， 並與 ESP8266 GND 共地 \n \n \n #include <SPI.h>          // 引入 SPI 通訊函式庫\n#include <nRF24L01.h>     // 引入 nRF24L01 無線模組定義\n#include <RF24.h>         // 引入 RF24 函式庫，方便操作 nRF24L01\n#include <Servo.h>        // 引入 Servo 函式庫，用來控制伺服馬達\n\n// 建立 RF24 物件，指定 CE 與 CSN 腳位 (ESP8266 的 D4 與 D8)\nRF24 radio(D4, D8);\n\n// 建立 Servo 物件\nServo myServo;\n\n// 無線通訊管道地址，必須與發送端一致\nconst byte address[6] = "00001";\n\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(115200);       // 初始化序列埠，方便除錯\n  myServo.attach(D1);         // 伺服訊號接 D1 (GPIO5)\n\n  // 初始化 nRF24L01 無線模組\n  radio.begin();\n  radio.openReadingPipe(0, address); // 開啟接收管道\n  radio.setPALevel(RF24_PA_LOW);     // 設定功率等級 (低功率)\n  radio.setDataRate(RF24_1MBPS);     // 設定傳輸速率 (1Mbps)\n  radio.setChannel(76);              // 設定頻道 (必須與發送端一致)\n  radio.startListening();            // 啟動接收模式\n\n  Serial.println("ESP8266 接收端啟動 - 等待按鈕訊號...");\n}\n\n// 用來存放接收到的按鈕狀態\nbool trigger = false;\n\nvoid loop() {\n  // 檢查是否有新的資料可讀取\n  if (radio.available()) {\n    radio.read(&trigger, sizeof(trigger)); // 讀取 trigger 狀態\n    Serial.println(trigger ? "收到：開始擺動" : "收到：停止擺動");\n  }\n\n  if (trigger) {\n    // 當 trigger 為 true → 伺服持續左右擺動\n    static int pos = 0;   // 當前角度\n    static int step = 4;  // 每次移動的角度增量\n\n    myServo.write(pos);   // 設定伺服角度\n    pos += step;          // 更新角度\n\n    // 當角度到達邊界 (0 或 180) → 改變方向\n    if (pos >= 180 || pos <= 0) step = -step;\n\n    delay(15);            // 控制擺動速度\n  }\n}\n \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'STM32F411 ESP8266 發送端程式與接收端程式.html'}, {'title': 'PTZ_TX', 'text': '發送端：STM32F411 Black Pill \n \n \n 單擊：磁力計校正 \n 雙擊：記錄當前零點並開始傳輸 \n 長按：鎖定伺服（傳送 0,0） \n \n \n \n \n \n 元件 \n 腳位 \n 說明 \n \n \n \n \n NRF24L01 VCC \n 3.3V \n 加100μF 電解電容\xa0 \n \n \n NRF24L01 GND \n GND \n - \n \n \n NRF24L01 CE \n PA1 \n - \n \n \n NRF24L01 CSN \n PA4 \n - \n \n \n NRF24L01 SCK \n PA5 \n SPI1 \n \n \n NRF24L01 MOSI \n PA7 \n SPI1 \n \n \n NRF24L01 MISO \n PA6 \n SPI1 \n \n \n 按鈕（Button） \n PA2 \n 另一端接 GND（使用內建上拉） \n \n \n LED（板載） \n PC13 \n 低電位亮 \n \n \n ADXL345 & HMC5883L \n SCL → PB8 SDA → PB9 \n I2C1 \n \n \n \n NRF24L01 注意：外接天線 PA+LNA 版本瞬間電流大，一定要在模組 VCC/GND 腳之間並聯 \xa0並聯一47uF電解電容，改善電源穩定性。 \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'PTZ_TX.html'}, {'title': 'code', 'text': '#include <Wire.h>\n#include <SPI.h>\n#include <RF24.h>\n#include <math.h>\n\n// ================== nRF24L01 ==================\n// CE=PA1, CSN=PA4, SCK=PA5, MOSI=PA7, MISO=PA6\nRF24 radio(PA1, PA4);\nconst byte address[6] = "00001";\n\n// ================== 感測器位址 ==================\n#define ADXL345_ADDR  0x53\n#define HMC5883L_ADDR 0x1E\n\n// ================== 按鈕 / LED ==================\n#define BTN_PIN  PA2\n#define LED_PIN  PC13  // 低電位亮\n\n// ================== 校正偏移 ==================\nint16_t accel_offset_x = 0, accel_offset_y = 0, accel_offset_z = 0;\nfloat   mag_offset_x = 0, mag_offset_y = 0;\n\n// ================== 零點 ==================\nfloat pitch_zero_offset = 0.0;\nfloat yaw_zero_offset   = 0.0;\n\n// ================== 狀態 ==================\nbool servo_active = false;\n\n// ================== 濾波 ==================\nfloat filtered_pitch = 0.0;\nfloat filtered_roll  = 0.0;\nfloat filtered_yaw   = 0.0;\nconst float alpha_pitch = 0.35;\nconst float alpha_roll  = 0.35;\nconst float alpha_yaw   = 0.35;\n\n// ================== 按鈕 ==================\nenum BtnEvent { BTN_NONE, BTN_SINGLE, BTN_DOUBLE, BTN_LONG };\nbool     btn_last_state   = HIGH;\nuint32_t btn_press_time   = 0;\nuint32_t btn_release_time = 0;\nuint8_t  btn_click_count  = 0;\nbool     btn_waiting      = false;\nconst uint16_t LONG_PRESS_MS = 1000;\nconst uint16_t DOUBLE_GAP_MS = 300;\nconst uint16_t DEBOUNCE_MS   = 20;\n\n// ================== LED 閃爍 ==================\nbool     led_blinking    = false;\nuint32_t led_last_toggle = 0;\nconst uint16_t BLINK_MS  = 300;\n\n// ================== 傳輸封包 ==================\nstruct AnglePacket {\n  float pitch;  // 俯仰角 -60~+60 度\n  float yaw;    // 偏航角 -60~+60 度\n};\n\nunsigned long lastTime = 0;\n\n// ==========================================\n//              函式宣告\n// ==========================================\nvoid     initADXL345();\nvoid     initHMC5883L();\nint16_t  readAxisLSB(byte addr, byte reg);\nvoid     readAccel(float &x_g, float &y_g, float &z_g);\nvoid     readMag(float &mx, float &my, float &mz);\nvoid     calibrateAccel();\nvoid     calibrateMag();\nvoid     recordZeroPoint();\nBtnEvent readButton();\nvoid     updateLED();\n\n// ==========================================\n//              Setup\n// ==========================================\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n  delay(1000);\n\n  // I2C\n  Wire.setSCL(PB8);\n  Wire.setSDA(PB9);\n  Wire.begin();\n  Wire.setClock(400000);          // Fast Mode 400kHz\n\n  // 按鈕 / LED\n  pinMode(BTN_PIN, INPUT_PULLUP);\n  pinMode(LED_PIN, OUTPUT);\n  digitalWrite(LED_PIN, HIGH);    // PC13 HIGH = 熄滅\n\n  // SPI 腳位指定（STM32 必須明確指定）\n  SPI.setMOSI(PA7);\n  SPI.setMISO(PA6);\n  SPI.setSCLK(PA5);\n  SPI.begin();\n\n  // nRF24L01 初始化，失敗時 LED 快閃\n  if (!radio.begin()) {\n    Serial.println("NRF24L01 初始化失敗！請檢查接線與電源");\n    while (1) {\n      digitalWrite(LED_PIN, !digitalRead(LED_PIN));\n      delay(100);\n    }\n  }\n\n  radio.setPALevel(RF24_PA_HIGH);  // HIGH 兼顧距離與穩定性\n  radio.setDataRate(RF24_1MBPS);   // 1MBPS 延遲低且距離足夠\n  radio.setChannel(108);           // 2.508GHz，避開 WiFi 干擾\n  radio.setRetries(0, 0);          // 關閉重傳，降低延遲\n  radio.setAutoAck(false);         // 單向廣播，不等 ACK\n  radio.setPayloadSize(8);         // 固定 8 bytes，省去協議開銷\n  radio.openWritingPipe(address);\n  radio.stopListening();           // TX 模式\n  Serial.println("nRF24L01 TX ready");\n\n  initADXL345();\n  initHMC5883L();\n  calibrateAccel();\n  calibrateMag();\n\n  Serial.println("=========================================");\n  Serial.println("單擊 = 磁力計校正");\n  Serial.println("雙擊 = 記錄零點並開始傳輸");\n  Serial.println("長按 = 鎖定 Servo (傳 0,0)");\n  Serial.println("=========================================");\n\n  lastTime = micros();\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              Loop\n// ==========================================\nvoid loop() {\n\n  // ── 按鈕事件 ──\n  BtnEvent evt = readButton();\n  if (evt == BTN_SINGLE) {\n    Serial.println(">> [單擊] 磁力計校正");\n    calibrateMag();\n  } else if (evt == BTN_DOUBLE) {\n    recordZeroPoint();\n    Serial.println(">> [雙擊] 記錄零點並開始");\n  } else if (evt == BTN_LONG) {\n    servo_active = false;\n    AnglePacket pkt = { 0.0, 0.0 };\n    radio.writeFast(&pkt, sizeof(pkt));\n    radio.txStandBy();\n    Serial.println(">> [長按] Servo 鎖定 90 度");\n  }\n\n  // ── LED 更新 ──\n  updateLED();\n\n  // ── 主迴圈 5ms（200Hz）──\n  if (micros() - lastTime >= 5000) {\n    lastTime += 5000;\n\n    // 讀取加速度計\n    float x_g, y_g, z_g;\n    readAccel(x_g, y_g, z_g);\n\n    // 俯仰、翻滾計算\n    float raw_pitch = atan2(-x_g, sqrt(y_g*y_g + z_g*z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n    float raw_roll  = atan2(y_g, z_g) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n    // 低通濾波\n    filtered_pitch = alpha_pitch * raw_pitch + (1.0 - alpha_pitch) * filtered_pitch;\n    filtered_roll  = alpha_roll  * raw_roll  + (1.0 - alpha_roll)  * filtered_roll;\n\n    // 讀取磁力計\n    float mx, my, mz;\n    readMag(mx, my, mz);\n\n    // 傾斜補償\n    float pitch_rad = filtered_pitch * PI / 180.0;\n    float roll_rad  = filtered_roll  * PI / 180.0;\n\n    float mx_h = mx * cos(pitch_rad)\n               + my * sin(roll_rad) * sin(pitch_rad)\n               - mz * cos(roll_rad) * sin(pitch_rad);\n    float my_h = my * cos(roll_rad)\n               + mz * sin(roll_rad);\n\n    // 偏航計算與濾波\n    float raw_yaw = atan2(-my_h, mx_h) * 180.0 / PI;\n    filtered_yaw  = alpha_yaw * raw_yaw + (1.0 - alpha_yaw) * filtered_yaw;\n\n    // 套用零點，限制範圍\n    float corrected_pitch = constrain(filtered_pitch - pitch_zero_offset, -60, 60);\n    float corrected_yaw   = constrain(filtered_yaw   - yaw_zero_offset,   -60, 60);\n\n    // 發射封包\n    if (servo_active) {\n      AnglePacket pkt = { corrected_pitch, corrected_yaw };\n      radio.writeFast(&pkt, sizeof(pkt));\n      radio.txStandBy();  // 確保發送完成再繼續\n    }\n\n    // Serial 節流：每 50ms 輸出一次\n    static uint32_t lastPrint = 0;\n    if (millis() - lastPrint >= 50) {\n      lastPrint = millis();\n      Serial.print("Pitch: "); Serial.print(corrected_pitch, 1);\n      Serial.print("  Yaw: "); Serial.print(corrected_yaw, 1);\n      Serial.print("  [");     Serial.print(servo_active ? "TX" : "LOCK");\n      Serial.println("]");\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              感測器初始化\n// ==========================================\nvoid initADXL345() {\n  // 0x2D = POWER_CTL，0x08 = Measurement Mode\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x2D); Wire.write(0x08);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n  // 0x31 = DATA_FORMAT，0x00 = ±2g 右對齊\n  Wire.beginTransmission(ADXL345_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x31); Wire.write(0x00);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n  Serial.println("ADXL345 ready");\n}\n\nvoid initHMC5883L() {\n  // 0x00 = Config A，0x70 = 8avg / 15Hz\n  Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x00); Wire.write(0x70);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n  // 0x01 = Config B，0x20 = Gain ±1.3Ga\n  Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x01); Wire.write(0x20);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n  // 0x02 = Mode，0x00 = Continuous\n  Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x02); Wire.write(0x00);\n  Wire.endTransmission();\n  Serial.println("HMC5883L ready");\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              感測器讀取\n// ==========================================\nint16_t readAxisLSB(byte addr, byte reg) {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(addr);\n  Wire.write(reg);\n  Wire.endTransmission(false);  // Repeated Start\n  Wire.requestFrom(addr, (uint8_t)2);\n  if (Wire.available() >= 2) {\n    byte lsb = Wire.read();\n    byte msb = Wire.read();\n    return (int16_t)((msb << 8) | lsb);\n  }\n  return 0;\n}\n\nvoid readAccel(float &x_g, float &y_g, float &z_g) {\n  // 扣除靜態偏移，除以 256 轉換為 g（±2g / 10-bit 模式）\n  x_g = (readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x32) - accel_offset_x) / 256.0;\n  y_g = (readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x34) - accel_offset_y) / 256.0;\n  z_g = (readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x36) - accel_offset_z) / 256.0;\n}\n\nvoid readMag(float &mx, float &my, float &mz) {\n  Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n  Wire.write(0x03);\n  Wire.endTransmission(false);\n  Wire.requestFrom(HMC5883L_ADDR, (uint8_t)6);\n  if (Wire.available() >= 6) {\n    // HMC5883L 暫存器順序：X → Z → Y（注意 Z 在 Y 前）\n    int16_t raw_mx = (Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read();\n    int16_t raw_mz = (Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read();\n    int16_t raw_my = (Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read();\n    mx = raw_mx - mag_offset_x;  // 扣除偏移\n    my = raw_my - mag_offset_y;\n    mz = raw_mz;\n  }\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              校正\n// ==========================================\nvoid calibrateAccel() {\n  Serial.println("加速度計校正中，保持靜止...");\n  long sum_x = 0, sum_y = 0, sum_z = 0;\n  for (int i = 0; i < 500; i++) {\n    sum_x += readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x32);\n    sum_y += readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x34);\n    sum_z += readAxisLSB(ADXL345_ADDR, 0x36);\n    delay(10);  // 500次 × 10ms = 約 5 秒\n  }\n  accel_offset_x = sum_x / 500;\n  accel_offset_y = sum_y / 500;\n  accel_offset_z = sum_z / 500 - 256;  // Z 軸扣除 1g 重力對應值\n  Serial.println("加速度計校正完成");\n}\n\nvoid calibrateMag() {\n  float mx_max = -99999, mx_min = 99999;\n  float my_max = -99999, my_min = 99999;\n\n  // 第一步：等待單擊，LED 閃爍\n  Serial.println("磁力計校正：單擊按鈕開始擺頭 5 次 ...");\n  led_blinking = true;\n  led_last_toggle = millis();\n  digitalWrite(LED_PIN, LOW);   // PC13 LOW = 亮\n\n  while (true) {\n    updateLED();\n    if (readButton() == BTN_SINGLE) break;\n  }\n\n  // 第二步：收資料，LED 長亮\n  Serial.println("開始擺頭 5 次！完成後單擊結束...");\n  led_blinking = false;\n  digitalWrite(LED_PIN, LOW);   // 長亮\n\n  while (true) {\n    updateLED();\n    if (readButton() == BTN_SINGLE) break;\n\n    Wire.beginTransmission(HMC5883L_ADDR);\n    Wire.write(0x03);\n    Wire.endTransmission(false);\n    Wire.requestFrom(HMC5883L_ADDR, (uint8_t)6);\n    if (Wire.available() >= 6) {\n      float raw_mx = (int16_t)((Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read());\n      (void)((Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read()); // 跳過 Z 軸\n      float raw_my = (int16_t)((Wire.read() << 8) | Wire.read());\n      mx_max = max(mx_max, raw_mx); mx_min = min(mx_min, raw_mx);\n      my_max = max(my_max, raw_my); my_min = min(my_min, raw_my);\n    }\n    delay(30);\n  }\n\n  // 完成，LED 熄滅\n  led_blinking = false;\n  digitalWrite(LED_PIN, HIGH);  // PC13 HIGH = 熄滅\n\n  float mx_range = mx_max - mx_min;\n  float my_range = my_max - my_min;\n  Serial.print("mx 範圍: "); Serial.print(mx_range);\n  Serial.print("  my 範圍: "); Serial.println(my_range);\n  if (mx_range < 50 || my_range < 50)\n    Serial.println("警告：擺頭角度可能不足，建議重新校正！");\n\n  mag_offset_x = (mx_max + mx_min) / 2.0;\n  mag_offset_y = (my_max + my_min) / 2.0;\n  Serial.print("Mag offset X: "); Serial.print(mag_offset_x);\n  Serial.print("  Y: ");          Serial.println(mag_offset_y);\n  Serial.println("磁力計校正完成");\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              零點記錄\n// ==========================================\nvoid recordZeroPoint() {\n  float x_g, y_g, z_g;\n  readAccel(x_g, y_g, z_g);\n  float mx, my, mz;\n  readMag(mx, my, mz);\n\n  pitch_zero_offset = atan2(-x_g, sqrt(y_g*y_g + z_g*z_g)) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n  float pitch_rad = pitch_zero_offset * PI / 180.0;\n  float roll_rad  = atan2(y_g, z_g);\n\n  float mx_h = mx * cos(pitch_rad)\n             + my * sin(roll_rad) * sin(pitch_rad)\n             - mz * cos(roll_rad) * sin(pitch_rad);\n  float my_h = my * cos(roll_rad)\n             + mz * sin(roll_rad);\n\n  yaw_zero_offset = atan2(-my_h, mx_h) * 180.0 / PI;\n\n  filtered_pitch = 0.0;\n  filtered_roll  = 0.0;\n  filtered_yaw   = 0.0;\n  servo_active   = true;\n\n  Serial.print(">> 零點完成 pitch_offset: "); Serial.print(pitch_zero_offset, 1);\n  Serial.print("  yaw_offset: ");             Serial.println(yaw_zero_offset, 1);\n  Serial.println(">> 開始發射角度訊號");\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              工具函式\n// ==========================================\nBtnEvent readButton() {\n  BtnEvent event = BTN_NONE;\n  bool state = digitalRead(BTN_PIN);\n  uint32_t now = millis();\n\n  // 下降邊緣：按下\n  if (btn_last_state == HIGH && state == LOW) {\n    delay(DEBOUNCE_MS);\n    if (digitalRead(BTN_PIN) == LOW) btn_press_time = now;\n  }\n\n  // 上升邊緣：放開\n  if (btn_last_state == LOW && state == HIGH) {\n    delay(DEBOUNCE_MS);\n    if (digitalRead(BTN_PIN) == HIGH) {\n      uint32_t held = now - btn_press_time;\n      if (held >= LONG_PRESS_MS) {\n        event = BTN_LONG;\n        btn_click_count = 0;\n        btn_waiting = false;\n      } else {\n        btn_click_count++;\n        btn_release_time = now;\n        btn_waiting = true;\n      }\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 雙擊視窗超時判斷\n  if (btn_waiting && (now - btn_release_time > DOUBLE_GAP_MS)) {\n    if (btn_click_count == 1) event = BTN_SINGLE;\n    if (btn_click_count >= 2) event = BTN_DOUBLE;\n    btn_click_count = 0;\n    btn_waiting = false;\n  }\n\n  btn_last_state = state;\n  return event;\n}\n\nvoid updateLED() {\n  if (led_blinking) {\n    if (millis() - led_last_toggle >= BLINK_MS) {\n      led_last_toggle = millis();\n      digitalWrite(LED_PIN, !digitalRead(LED_PIN));\n    }\n  }\n} \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'code.html'}, {'title': 'PTZ_RX', 'text': '接收端：NodeMCU V3 ESP8266 \n \n \n \n 元件 \n 腳位 \n 說明 \n \n \n \n \n NRF24L01 VCC \n 3.3V \n 加 100μF 電容 \n \n \n NRF24L01 GND \n GND \n - \n \n \n NRF24L01 CE \n D4 (GPIO2) \n - \n \n \n NRF24L01 CSN \n D8 (GPIO15) \n - \n \n \n NRF24L01 SCK \n D5 (GPIO14) \n - \n \n \n NRF24L01 MOSI \n D7 (GPIO13) \n - \n \n \n NRF24L01 MISO \n D6 (GPIO12) \n - \n \n \n Pitch Servo 訊號 \n D1 (GPIO5) \n - \n \n \n Yaw Servo 訊號 \n D2 (GPIO4) \n - \n \n \n Servo VCC（紅線） \n 獨立 5V \n 使用獨立電源 \n \n \n Servo GND（黑/棕線） \n GND \n 必須與 NodeMCU GND 共地 \n \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'PTZ_RX.html'}, {'title': 'code2', 'text': '// ==========================================\n// 接收端：NodeMCU ESP8266\n// 功能：透過 nRF24L01 接收 STM32 傳來的\n//       Pitch / Yaw 角度，控制兩個伺服馬達\n// ==========================================\n\n\n#include <SPI.h>\n#include <nRF24L01.h>\n#include <RF24.h>\n#include <Servo.h>\n\n// ================== nRF24L01 ==================\n// CE=D4(GPIO2), CSN=D8(GPIO15)\n// SCK=D5(GPIO14), MOSI=D7(GPIO13), MISO=D6(GPIO12)\nRF24 radio(D4, D8);\nconst byte address[6] = "00001";  // 必須與發射端完全相同\n\n// ================== Servo ==================\nServo pitchServo;  // D1 (GPIO5)\nServo yawServo;    // D2 (GPIO4)\n\n// ================== 傳輸封包 ==================\n// 必須與發射端結構完全一致，共 8 bytes\nstruct AnglePacket {\n  float pitch;  // 俯仰角 -60~+60 度\n  float yaw;    // 偏航角 -60~+60 度\n};\n\n// ================== 接收端濾波 ==================\n// 補償無線偶發跳值，alpha 與發射端獨立\nfloat last_pitch = 0.0;\nfloat last_yaw   = 0.0;\nconst float alpha = 0.5;  // 0.3~0.6，越大反應越快\n\n// ==========================================\n//              Setup\n// ==========================================\nvoid setup() {\n  Serial.begin(115200);\n\n\n\n  // Servo 初始化\n  // 500~2400us 脈衝範圍，相容大多數舵機\n  pitchServo.attach(D1, 500, 2400);  // GPIO5\n  yawServo.attach(D2, 500, 2400);    // GPIO4\n  pitchServo.write(90);              // 上電歸中\n  yawServo.write(90);\n  Serial.println("Servo ready (D1=Pitch, D2=Yaw)");\n\n  // nRF24L01 初始化\nradio.begin();\n  radio.setPALevel(RF24_PA_HIGH);     // ← 與發送端一致\n  radio.setDataRate(RF24_1MBPS);      // ← 改成 1MBPS\n  radio.setChannel(108);\n  radio.setAutoAck(false);\n  radio.setPayloadSize(8);\n  radio.openReadingPipe(0, address);\n  radio.startListening();\n\n  Serial.println("nRF24L01 RX ready (HIGH + 1MBPS)");\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n//              Loop\n// ==========================================\nvoid loop() {\n\n  // 有封包就立即處理（非阻塞）\n  if (radio.available()) {\n    AnglePacket pkt;\n    radio.read(&pkt, sizeof(pkt));  // 讀取 8 bytes\n\n    // 低通濾波：平滑偶發跳值\n    last_pitch = alpha * pkt.pitch + (1.0 - alpha) * last_pitch;\n    last_yaw   = alpha * pkt.yaw   + (1.0 - alpha) * last_yaw;\n\n    // 角度映射：-60~+60 度 → Servo 45~135 度\n    // 保留機械緩衝，避免撞到極限位置\n    // 建議把 constrain 改成 float 版本，避免精度損失\n    int sp = map(constrain(last_pitch, -60.0f, 60.0f), -60, 60, 45, 135);\n    int sy = map(constrain(last_yaw,   -60.0f, 60.0f), -60, 60, 45, 135);\n\n    pitchServo.write(sp);\n    yawServo.write(sy);\n\n    // Serial 節流：每 50ms 輸出一次\n    static uint32_t lastPrint = 0;\n    if (millis() - lastPrint >= 50) {\n      lastPrint = millis();\n      Serial.print("Pitch: "); Serial.print(last_pitch, 1);\n      Serial.print("  Yaw: "); Serial.print(last_yaw, 1);\n      Serial.print("  SP: ");  Serial.print(sp);\n      Serial.print("  SY: ");  Serial.println(sy);\n    }\n  }\n}', 'tags': '', 'url': 'code2.html'}, {'title': 'problem', 'text': '', 'tags': '', 'url': 'problem.html'}, {'title': 'Brython', 'text': 'https://brython.info/ \xa0 \n 從 1 累加到 100: \n 1 add to 100 ROC Flag PROC flag USA Flag GD in Brython \n  導入 brython 程式庫  \n \n \n \n \n  啟動 Brython  \n \n \n \n  導入 FileSaver 與 filereader  \n \n \n \n \n  導入 ace  \n \n \n \n \n \n \n  導入 gearUtils-0.9.js Cango 齒輪繪圖程式庫  \n \n \n \n \n \n \n  請注意, 這裡使用 Javascript 將 localStorage["kw_py_src1"] 中存在近端瀏覽器的程式碼, 由使用者決定存檔名稱 \n \n \n \n \n \n \n  add 1 to 100 開始  \n \n \n  add 1 to 100 結束 \n  editor1 開始  \n  用來顯示程式碼的 editor 區域  \n \n  以下的表單與按鈕與前面的 Javascript doSave 函式以及 FileSaver.min.js 互相配合  \n  存擋表單開始  \n Filename:  .py   \n  存擋表單結束  \n \n  執行與清除按鈕開始  \n Run   Output   清除輸出區 清除繪圖區 Reload \n  執行與清除按鈕結束  \n \n  程式執行 ouput 區  \n \n  Brython 程式執行的結果, 都以 brython_div1 作為切入位置  \n \n  editor1 結束   ##########################################  \n 從 1 累加到 100 part2: \n 1 add to 100 cango_three_gears BSnake AI Tetris Rotating Block \n  請注意, 這裡使用 Javascript 將 localStorage["kw_py_src2"] 中存在近端瀏覽器的程式碼, 由使用者決定存檔名稱 \n \n \n \n  add 1 to 100 part2 開始  \n \n \n  add 1 to 100 part2 結束 \n  editor2 開始  \n  用來顯示程式碼的 editor 區域  \n \n  以下的表單與按鈕與前面的 Javascript doSave 函式以及 FileSaver.min.js 互相配合  \n  存擋表單開始  \n Filename:  .py   \n  存擋表單結束  \n \n  執行與清除按鈕開始  \n Run   Output   清除輸出區 清除繪圖區 Reload \n  執行與清除按鈕結束  \n \n  程式執行 ouput 區  \n \n  Brython 程式執行的結果, 都以 brython_div1 作為切入位置  \n \n  editor2 結束  \n \n \n', 'tags': '', 'url': 'Brython.html'}]};